{"tid":1310952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉：不認同改組行會 已含不同光譜成員","createTime":"2019-07-13T02:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T06:30:20.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f197a2b2e5158b1b65fcd6ff3ad7acd04deb3fd4","tid":1310952,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:47:27.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀在一個電台節目上表示，不認同改組行政會議，指現屆行政會議已經<span style=\"color: red;\">包括不同光譜的成員</span>，有人熟悉金融、安老等範疇，召集人陳智思亦與泛民有聯絡，<span style=\"color: red;\">反問行會還需要哪些人才</span>。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀重申，<span style=\"color: red;\">行政會議所有成員都是支持政府修訂《逃犯條例》，假如她和湯家驊因為較常向公眾解畫，就被要求辭職是無道理。</span><br />\n<br />\n她又稱，贊成政府重新建立<span style=\"color: red;\">中央政策組</span>，為政府擔任智囊，以及為不同政治顏色的學者提供平台表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n對於另一名行會成員<span style=\"color: blue;\">羅范椒芬</span>指出，假如<span style=\"color: red;\">有官員自願下台未嘗不是好事</span>，葉劉淑儀則稱，這個講法是「<span style=\"color: red;\">講就容易</span>」，認為單憑一兩個官員下台，不能解決問題，亦怕愈換愈差，而改革管治風格才能夠幫助香港走出困局。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2190879/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2190879%2F&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=95c0d8db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2190879/</a>"},{"pid":"51aeebd888c1688ba42f3dfa45b5a739e102c437","tid":1310952,"uid":155095,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"葉劉自己同林鄭就係唔同光譜啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/08170617/template24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F08170617%2Ftemplate24.png&h=f1b6f1ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc1a9fd2d940005019e22dc2c1fb4a547e7dbbe0","tid":1310952,"uid":196924,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於另一名行會成員羅范椒芬指出，假如有官員自願下台未嘗不是好事，葉劉淑儀則稱，這個講法是「講就容易」